```
POLICE_SHIFT4PAYMENTS_00001233
SHIFT4 PAYMENTS ANNOUNCES ACQUISITION OF MERCHANT LINK, VANTIV
AND SHIFT4 ANNOUNCE AGREEMENT
Shift4 Payments today announced its acquisition of Merchant Link, a leading payment gateway
provider, and an agreement with Vantiv, now Worldpay, to provide EMV and tokenization to
Worldpay's customers.
LAS VEGAS -- January 15, 2018 -- Shift4 Payments today announced that it has acquired
Merchant Link, a leading payment gateway provider with more than 200,000 merchants and 30+
processor/acquirer integrations, from private equity firm Welsh, Carson, Anderson & Stowe. In
the past 6 months, Shift4 Payments has also acquired and integrated three other payment
technology companies -- four acquisitions in total.
With today's announcement, Shift4 Payments now offers the most comprehensive payment
solution in the marketplace, including:
The top technology solutions for merchant acquisition, point of sale, payment processing,
and more
The best technologies across point-to-point encryption (P2PE), tokenization, EMV, and
cyber-security -- the industry's best data security solution available
Support for every payment method, including all major credit and debit brands, private-
label, and most alternative and mobile
Integrations to all major processors/acquirers in the United States, including
connections to Vantiv, Chase Paymentech, First Data, Worldpay, TSYS, Elavon, and
Global Payments
Connections to all major PIN debit networks
In-house customer support and 24/7/365 availability
Merchant Link provides payment gateway services to a wide range of leading lodging, retail,
and food and beverage customers, including a number of multi-chain brands.
“This acquisition truly solidifies Shift4 Payments as a leading provider of payment technology
throughout North America," said Jared Isaacman, CEO of Shift4 Payments. "Merchant Link's
connectivity to every major processor, expertise in numerous verticals, and strong
relationships with leading ISVs make this a very strategic fit for Shift4 Payments."
In a separate release today, Shift4 Payments and Vantiv, now Worldpay, announced a
partnership to bring EMV and tokenization to Worldpay's customers. The new partnership will
allow Worldpay to deliver a seamless, secure, and unified EMV solution to its joint ISV clients.
```

```
POLICE_SHIFT4PAYMENTS_00001234
About Shift4 Payments
Shift4 Payments is the leader in secure payment processing solutions, powering the top POS
and PMS systems across numerous verticals, including Food & Beverage, Hospitality, Lodging,
Gaming, Retail, and e-Commerce. Serving more than 200,000 merchants and 33,000 partners in
North America, the company securely processes over 1 billion transactions annually,
representing over $100 billion in payments each year. For additional information, visit
www.shift4.com.
About Merchant Link
Merchant Link is a leading provider of cloud-based payment gateway and data security
solutions, removing the risk, cost and burden of PCI compliance for more than 200,000
merchant locations. Founded in 1993 and headquartered in Silver Spring, MD, we currently
enable more than 6 billion transactions annually for some of the world's best-known merchants,
providing connectivity to the major U.S. payment processors.
```
